data.description: NEWLY RENOVATED/UPDATED Large, 4-bedroom 3-Bath corner home! This home has fresh interior and exterior painting, brand new stainless steel appliances, updated hardware and NEW LTV flooring and all new carpet installed. HVAC/Heating system newly updated. Features a bottom patio and large deck overlooking the large beautiful backyard that has endless possibilities. Wireless garage access via MyQ. WON'T LAST LONG! GREAT OPPORTUNITY. MOVE-IN READY HOME. Located near several shops in dining in the Covington/Conyers area - Located only 35-40 minutes from Downtown Atlanta.
